{"fadein":1.5,"once":true,"id":"BIRUI2","fadeType":2,"mode":2,"fadeOut":1.5,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"sequence":[["Hiei's Banquet\n\n<size=45>Chapter 2: A Formal Invitation<\/size>",1]],"stopbgm":true},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"flashin":{"black":true,"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0]},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":2,"flashout":{"black":true,"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1]},"bgm":"story-1","nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I'm in... an especially good mood? And you're curious as to why?","dir":1,"bgmDelay":2,"actor":304020},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"\"Did something good happen,\" huh...? It's as you say, but... I suppose you forgot, Commander. Actually...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":304020},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I finally found it, Hiei. I almost forgot that you were the secretary today... Ahem! I've managed to get everything that you asked for.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":304010},{"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"side":0,"say":"Oh my. Thank you for all your help~","paintingFadeOut":{"time":0.5,"side":1},"dir":1,"nameColor":"#a9f548","actor":304020},{"side":1,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I'm also looking forward to it. I've never been disappointed by an event you've hosted.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":304010},{"side":0,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"I'm glad to hear that.","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":304020},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"And Commander, this is for you. Since you're already in the room, I might as well give it to you directly...","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":304010},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Kongou handed me a white envelope with golden lace. It seemed like an invitation of some sort.","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Sorry for the formalities, but there's a certain way we have to do these things~â™ª","dir":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":304020},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"When I opened the envelope, I found a small card inside.","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Upon the card were several lines of carefully handwritten words.","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Commander, we cordially invite you","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"to attend the upcoming banquet to be held at 7 PM this Saturday.","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"We hope that you will be able to take time out of your busy schedule to attend.","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"I do hope to see you there.","dir":1},{"side":2,"bgName":"bg_story_task","typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"say":"Sincerely, Hiei","blackBg":true,"dir":1}]}